{"tid":1384953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]東華響應罷工","createTime":"2019-07-30T03:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T03:35:55.000Z","uid":291031,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7d6dd6337f85aa38c3480bbe353e7ab16b45a62b","tid":1384953,"uid":291031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:32:25.000Z","msg":"SORRY 標題黨, 呃左大家入黎<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正式宣佈東華三院社會運動關注組即日成立</span></span></div><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/東華三院社會運動關注組-105220120821199/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F%E6%9D%B1%E8%8F%AF%E4%B8%89%E9%99%A2%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%B5%84-105220120821199%2F&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmuL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=640bc0e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/東華三院社會運動關注組-105220120821199/</a><br />\n<br />\n過去50日，眼見社會充斥著不公義的事件，政府繼續漠視民意，拒絕回應五大訴求、警方濫暴、多名遊行或示威人士受傷和被捕，甚至元朗區有暴徒無差別的襲擊市民，我們實在無法再容易此等事件再發生。<br />\n<br />\n作為社會工作員，我們堅守社工守則。我們有責任維護人權及促進社會公義，並相信任何社會都應為其公民謀取最大的福祉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">為履行社會公義，我們決定於2019年8月5日發起罷工，以表達對極權政府的不滿。</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BQ4vYZC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBQ4vYZC.png&h=583f57c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b72a8eccc07964cf957de0b789305ad635ac5c7","tid":1384953,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}